1. *Timu* je tokom trke iznenadila neočekivana promena vremena. (The team was surprised by an unexpected change of weather during the race.)

2. Lider *timu*a je zatražio da se sastanemo u petak. (The leader of the team asked us to meet on Friday.)

3. Učenici *timu*a su dobili sertifikat za uspešno završen kurs. (The members of the team got a certificate for successfully completing the course.)

4. *Timu* se nada da će uspeti da ostvari svoj cilj. (The team is hoping to achieve its goal.)

5. *Timu* čine četvoro ljudi sa različitim iskustvom. (The team consists of four people with different experience.)